### Stash-pop verification

`git stash` of all `src/`, `prisma/`, `tests/` changes (excluding the
new untracked `v184_homepage_visibility.test.ts`); ran the new file
against the pre-change tree:

```
FAIL  tests/unit/v184_homepage_visibility.test.ts (35 tests | 25 failed)
Tests  25 failed | 10 passed (35)
```

25/35 fail on the broken state — the new tests are genuine
regression-target tests, not pass-on-anything assertions. The 10 that
still pass cover surfaces unrelated to the v1.84.0 changes (legacy
`setLeagueRecruiting` shape, the in-place not-recruiting testid, etc).

